<plot>Frank is working away in his clock shop,but can't shake the feeling that someone is keeping time with his wife, Helen. Little things arouse suspicion and keep creeping into his conscience. What will he do if his worst fears become realized? In this psychological mystery you enter Frank's world as he tries to sort out a solution to his problem - a problem that could have fatal consequences when the clock strikes Four O'Clock.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?201556</url></doc>
